    <li>Diagnosis Algorithm </li>
    <li>Management Algorithm </li>
    <li>Cardiovascular Risk Management Algorithm </li>
</ul>
<p>Additionally, an algorithm titled "Treatment of Diabetic Nephropathy" is provided in Appendix B in the original guideline document (see the "Guideline Availability" field).</p></div></p>

